Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), zig (>= 0.14.1), libgtk-4-dev, libgtk4-layer-shell-dev, libadwaita-1-dev, gettext, libxml2-utils, blueprint-compiler (>= 0.16.0)

Package: ghostty
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: GPU-accelerated terminal emulator with advanced features
 Ghostty is a cross-platform, GPU-accelerated terminal emulator designed for
 performance, compatibility, and extensibility. It supports modern features like
 ligatures, custom shaders, and real-time rendering while maintaining
 compatibility with traditional terminal applications.
 This package provides the Ghostty terminal emulator built with Zig 0.14.1.
